title: Taylor Swift’s Second-Week Sales Are Still Among the Year’s Biggest
description: The singer’s blockbuster new album, “Midnights,” holds strong atop the Billboard 200 chart, and her single “Anti-Hero” is No. 1 on the Hot 100.
dc:creator: Joe Coscarelli
media:description: Taylor Swift has coasted to a second week atop the charts, as “Midnights” earned the equivalent of another 342,000 album sales.
